==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Recuperate
<hw>Re*cu"per*ate</hw> <pr>(-?t)</pr>, <pos>v. i.</pos>
<vmorph>[<pos>imp. & p. p.</pos> <conjf>Recuperated</conjf>
<pr>(-?`t?d)</pr>; <pos>p. pr. & vb. n.</pos>
<conjf>Recuperating</conjf>.]</vmorph> <ety>[L. <ets>recuperatus</ets>,
p. p. of <ets>recuperare</ets>. See <er>Recover</er> to get
again.]</ety> <def>To recover health; to regain strength; to
convalesce.</def>⟦br⟧
